headline: Kraft Heinz (KHC) Valuation Check as Steve Cahillane Takes Helm to Steer Planned Corporate Split
summary: Kraft Heinz (KHC) just handed the keys to Steve Cahillane, the executive who helped split Kellogg and build Kellanova, right as it prepares its own breakup into two standalone companies. See our latest analysis for Kraft Heinz.
